    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior shows no scratches, dents, or blemishes, and the finish is clean and unmarked. The interior is spotless with no signs of wear on any surfaces or upholstery. Mechanically the vehicle is in excellent working order with no known issues.",
